# 9. Docker Network

One of the biggest advantages.

Compose automatically creates a private network.

```text
Frontend

↓

Backend

↓

Database
```

No need to know IP addresses.

Backend connects using

```text
db
```

instead of

```text
192.168.x.x
```

This is called **Docker DNS**.

---

# Real Example

Backend configuration

```text
Host=db
```

NOT

```text
Host=localhost
```

Because backend and database are in different containers.

---

# 10. Environment Variables

Example

```text
POSTGRES_DB

POSTGRES_USER

POSTGRES_PASSWORD
```

Purpose

