---

# 11. Health Checks

One of the most useful features.

Instead of simply checking

```text
Container Running
```

Compose checks

```text
Application Working?
```

Example

```text
Database accepts connections?

YES

↓

Healthy
```

---

# Why Health Checks?

Suppose PostgreSQL takes 20 seconds to initialize.

Backend starts immediately.

Backend tries to connect.

Connection fails.

Health check prevents this.

---

Flow

```text
Database Starting

↓

Health Check

↓

Healthy

↓

Backend Starts
```

---

