# 14. Problems We Faced

## Problem 1

Frontend Build Failed

Reason

Dockerfile mistake.

```text
RUN RUN npm install
```

Solution

Removed duplicate RUN.

---

## Problem 2

Docker Engine Not Running

Error

```text
error during connect
```

Root Cause

Docker Desktop stopped.

Solution

Started Docker Desktop.

---

## Problem 3

Backend Already Running

Error

```text
EADDRINUSE

5000
```

Root Cause

PM2 already running backend.

Solution

Stopped old process.

---

## Problem 4

Container Cannot Connect to Database

Root Cause

Wrong hostname.

Correct

```text
db
```

Wrong

```text
localhost
```

